{"lemma":"ثَلاثِ","slug":"ثَلاثِ","root":"ثلث","root_slug":"ثلث","root_link":"/words/roots/ثلث","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ثَلاث","root":"ثلث","pos":"N","occurrence_count":8},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adv","num"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4624","n4625","n4626"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AB%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"num","gloss":"masculine of ثَلَاثَة (ṯalāṯa, “three”)","tags":["form-of","masculine"]},{"pos":"adv","gloss":"three at a time, in a group of three, in threes","examples":[{"text":"الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ فَاطِرِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ جَاعِلِ الْمَلَائِكَةِ رُسُلًا أُولِي أَجْنِحَةٍ مَّثْنَىٰ وَثُلَاثَ وَرُبَاعَ ۚ يَزِيدُ فِي الْخَلْقِ مَا يَشَاءُ ۚ إِنَّ اللَّهَ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/θa.laːθ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4624","headword_ar":"ثَلَاثٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", also written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"val`vN","text_ar":"ثَلٰثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in six places: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvu","text_ar":"ثُلَاثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4625","headword_ar":"ثُلَاثُ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavolavu","text_ar":"مَثْلَثُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Three and three; three and three together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three at a time and three at a time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) imperfectly decl. [because] changed from the original form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or because of their having the quality of epithets and deviating from the original form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": they are epithets; for you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mararotu biqawomK","text_ar":"مَرَرْتُ بِقَوْمٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavonaY wavulaAva","text_ar":"مَثْنَى وَثُلَاثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I passed by a party of men two and two, and three and three, together"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Sb, S:) or they are imperfectly decl. because they deviate from their original as to the letter and the meaning; the original word being changed as above stated, and the meaning being changed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulay~ivN","text_ar":"ثُلَيِّثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", perfectly decl., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uHay~idN","text_ar":"اُحَيِّدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., because it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humay~irN","text_ar":"حُمَيِّرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaArN","text_ar":"حِمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], assuming the form of that which is perfectly decl., though it is not so in the cases of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHosanu","text_ar":"اَحْسَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the like, as these words, in assuming the dim. form, do not deviate from the measure of a verb, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^uHayosinahu","text_ar":"مَا اُحَيْسِنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[How goodly is he!] is sometimes said. (S.) It is said in the Kur [iv. 3],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA@nokiHuwA maA TaAba","text_ar":"فَا@نْكِحُوا مَا طَابَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lakumo mina Aln~isaA='i wavulaAva warubaAEa","text_ar":"لَكُمْ مِنَ النِّسَا=ءِ وَثُلَاثَ وَرُبَاعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then marry ye such as please you, of women, two"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two, and three"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three, and four"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two at a time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:] here"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mvnY","text_ar":"مثنى"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. are imperfectly decl. because deviating from the original form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aivonayoni Aivonayoni","text_ar":"اِثْنَيْنِ اِثْنَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c., and from the fem. form. (Zj, T, L.) And one says ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavolava mavolava","text_ar":"مَثْلَثَ مَثْلَثَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAva vulaAva","text_ar":"ثُلَاثَ ثُلَاثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalotu Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"فَعَلْتُ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavonaY wavulaAva warubaAEa","text_ar":"مَثْنَى وَثُلَاثَ وَرُبَاعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did the thing twice and twice, and thrice and thrice, and four times and four times."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvN","text_ar":"ثُلَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is app. fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvapN","text_ar":"ثُلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a dial, var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the fem. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw vulaAvK","text_ar":"ذُو ثُلَاثٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm [to the initial"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"v","text_ar":"ث"},{"kind":"text","text":"], A camel's ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"girth of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDiyn","text_ar":"وَضِين"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ailotaqato EuraA *iY vulaAvihaA","text_ar":"اِلْتَقَتْ عُرَا ذِى ثُلَاثِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [lit.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The loops of her girth met together"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (A, TA; [but in a copy of the former, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Y valaAvihaA","text_ar":"ذى ثَلَاثِهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, lean"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lank in the belly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A. [See a similar saying voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biTaAnN","text_ar":"بِطَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"waqado Damarato Hat~aY badaA *uw vulaAvihaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And she had become lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lank in the belly, so that her girth appeared"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*w","text_ar":"ذو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlAvhA","text_ar":"ثلاثها"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her belly, and the two skins,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[namely,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the upper, and that which is pared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scraped off, after the flaying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or, accord. to some, the phrase is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hat~aY A@rotaqaY *w vlAvhA","text_ar":"حَتَّى ا@رْتَقَى ذو ثلاثها"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that her fœtus rose"},{"kind":"text","text":"to her back; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlAv","text_ar":"ثلاث"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here again in a copy of the A written with fet-h to the initial"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"v","text_ar":"ث"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlAvhA","text_ar":"ثلاثها"},{"kind":"text","text":",] being the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiyaA='","text_ar":"سَابِيَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salaA","text_ar":"سَلَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the womb. (A, TA.) You say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi *uw valaAvK","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ ذُو ثَلَاثٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [so I find it written, but perhaps it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*w vulaAvK","text_ar":"ذو ثُلَاثٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Upon him is a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of the wool of three sheep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA. [In the latter without any syll. sign to show that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlAv","text_ar":"ثلاث"},{"kind":"text","text":"here differs from the form in the exs. cited before.])"}],"source_refs":["S","L","K","Sb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4626","headword_ar":"ثِلَاث","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaAlivN","text_ar":"ثَالِثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}